If any malfunction or problems in the application developer to inform the post office. The app contains unobtrusive advertisements.
The order of activation Horses Amazing Live Wallpaper:
1. To download the application Horses Amazing Live Wallpaper on the device.
2. Sign in to the device settings menu and activate the animated wallpaper.
3. When the application is finished loading, you can view it in the preview window. - Select the download button below the window and start the live wallpaper on your home screen.
